<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25547</anchor> <rss>anon.150.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Proof</taxon> <addr>anon.150</addr>  <route>anon.150.xml</route>    </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>We proceed by induction on the <link href="erct-001F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001F" title="Indexing of truncation levels">truncation level</link> <tex>n</tex>: when <tex>n=-2</tex>, we recall that the <link href="erct-002U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002U" title="The identity map is contractible">identity map is contractible</link>, and in the inductive step we apply the <link href="erct-002T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002T" title="Truncation is upward closed">upward closure of <tex>n</tex>-truncation</link> to each <link href="erct-001Q.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001Q" title="Fiber">fiber</link> of <tex>1_{ A }</tex>.</p>
</mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25548</anchor> <rss>erct-002V.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-002V</addr>  <route>erct-002V.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>The identity map is <span style="white-space: nowrap"><tex>n</tex>-truncated</span> for all <tex>n</tex></title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002V.agda" type="external">erct-002V.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>For any type <tex>A</tex>, the identity map <tex>1_{ A } \colon  A \to  A</tex> is <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map"><span style="white-space: nowrap"><tex>n</tex>-truncated</span></link> for all <tex>n</tex>.</p>
 
   
   
 
</mainmatter> </tree></context> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25549</anchor> <rss>erct-002T.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-002T</addr>  <route>erct-002T.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-001G.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001G" title="N-truncated type">Truncation</link> is upward closed</title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002T.agda" type="external">erct-002T.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>If a type <tex>A</tex> is <link href="erct-001G.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001G" title="N-truncated type"><span style="white-space: nowrap"><tex>n</tex>-truncated</span></link>, then it is also <link href="erct-001G.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001G" title="N-truncated type"><tex>n+1</tex>-truncated</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25550</anchor> <rss>anon.152.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Proof</taxon> <addr>anon.152</addr>  <route>anon.152.xml</route>    </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>We proceed by induction on the <link href="erct-001F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001F" title="Indexing of truncation levels">truncation level</link> <tex>n</tex>, with two base cases:</p>
 <ul><li>If <tex>n=-2</tex>, we recall that <link href="erct-001K.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001K" title="Contractible types are propositions">contractible types are propositions</link>.</li>
  <li>If <tex>n=-1</tex>, we recall that <link href="erct-001L.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001L" title="Propositions are sets">propositions are sets</link>.</li></ul>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25551</anchor> <rss>erct-002U.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-002U</addr>  <route>erct-002U.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>The identity map is <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link></title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002U.agda" type="external">erct-002U.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>For any type <tex>A</tex>, the identity map <tex>1_{ A } \colon  A \to  A</tex> is <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25552</anchor> <rss>anon.151.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Proof</taxon> <addr>anon.151</addr>  <route>anon.151.xml</route>    </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>Immediate by identification induction.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25553</anchor> <rss>erct-001Q.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-001Q</addr>  <route>erct-001Q.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>20</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Fiber</title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001Q.agda" type="external">erct-001Q.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>The <em><strong>fiber</strong></em> of a function <tex>f \colon  A  \to  B</tex> at an element <tex>b:B</tex> is the type consisting of elements <tex>a \colon  A</tex> equipped with identifications <tex>p \colon  fa=b</tex>.</p></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>25554</anchor> <rss>erct-001F.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Convention</taxon> <addr>erct-001F</addr>  <route>erct-001F.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>20</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Indexing of truncation levels</title> <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001F.agda" type="external">erct-001F.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A <em><strong>truncation level</strong></em> is an integer <tex>n  \geq  -2</tex>.</p></mainmatter> </tree></related> <backlinks/> <references/></backmatter></tree>